content: People - Center for Artificial Intelligence and Data Science Intern Animation stoppen Center for Artificial Intelligence and Data Science CAIDAS is headed by an executive board consisting of five members. One of the executive board's members acts as CAIDAS' spokeperson. The executive board is supported by an administrative office. The heads of chairs and research groups are regular members of CAIDAS.
